overview:
The continued success of West Island International Trucks can be attributed to a versatile and motivated team of the best truck professionals in Montreal. We understand that our obligation to providing you with quality service and products starts with investing in our employees through performance improvements and on-going training. Coupled with the latest in technology and truck equipment, our Montreal facility provides our employees with the tools they need to control the quality of our products and services.

Our mission is to become the number one truck dealership in Montreal and Quebec by providing the best service and products to guarantee your satisfaction. Our vision is to help Quebec companies excel by providing quality new and used trucks, leasing options, a responsive service, truck equipment, parts and truck repair service.
